rences','2','1251534480QHPE'),('This website has been added to your site manager.','2','1251770410PASS'),('This website could not be added.','2','1251770410PAST'),('Refresh all licenses','1','1251857784QRWO'),('Could not identify your website URL.','2','1251905717NHWT'),('Your website was not found. Please contract support.','2','1251905717NHWU'),('The licenses have been updated!','2','1251905717NHWW'),('There is a problem with the Localhost license.','2','1251905718PEOQ'),('The license could not be installed for $APPLICATION because the application is not yet installed.','2','1251905719IQBZ'),('The license could not be installed for application: $APPLICATION','2','1251905719IQCA'),('No licenses were found for this website.','2','1251912852OWAG'),('An error occur while installing the licenses!','2','1251959063BNBJ'),('Click Yes to force \"https\" secure internet on the Back-End.','1','1251988094BIBR'),('File Size','1','1252569179LCYI'),('File Name','1','1252569179LCYJ'),('User Logs','1','1252569179LCYK'),('User Log Details','1','1252569179LCYL'),('User Logs Details','1','1252569180FERI'),('Log Download','1','1252894206NMXU'),('User Log Delete','1','1252894206NMXV'),('Logs','2','1253200893CXZC'),('Click Yes to force \"https\" secure internet on the Front-End.','1','1254100130KOZM'),('Click No to turn off any communication with external website.<br>Note: turning this option Off will disable application updates and limit some of the functionality of the site. <br>','1','1254100130KOZN'),('Force SSL Front-End','1','1254100130KOZO'),('Force SSL Back-End','1','1254100130KOZP'),('The system can also try to use the Framework ( Joomla, Wordpress, etc ) detected language if it is available for joobi applications. By default, this is done after the other detection systems, thus, its ordering value is 3. If you set its ordering lower than the others, the system will use the framework language if available.','1','1257940976WWP'),('There are no logs available at this time. Please